'''数学突破奖'''（Breakthrough Prize in Mathematics）是2013年由[[尤里·米尔纳|尤里·米尔纳]]与[[马克·扎克伯格|马克·扎克伯格]]共同设立的奖项<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://breakthroughprize.org/?controller=Page&action=prize&p=3 |title=Breakthrough Prize in MATHEMATICS |access-date=2014-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728143746/https://breakthroughprize.org/?controller=Page&action=prize&p=3 |archive-date=2014-07-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2016届开始在突破奖外还颁发新视野奖。

第一届于2014年（2015年奖，前一年颁发）颁发给[[西蒙·唐纳森|西蒙·唐纳森]]、[[马克西姆·孔采维奇|马克西姆·孔采维奇]]、[[雅各·卢里|雅各·卢里]]、[[陶哲轩|陶哲轩]]与[[理查·泰勒_(数学家)|理查·泰勒]]，之后每一年有一位获奖者，每位获奖者各得300万美元<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/23/us/the-multimillion-dollar-minds-of-5-mathematical-masters.html |title=''New York Times'', 23 June 2014, ''The Multimillion-Dollar Minds of 5 Mathematical Masters'' |accessdate=2014-06-23 |archive-date=2014-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140623230342/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/23/us/the-multimillion-dollar-minds-of-5-mathematical-masters.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=澳洲華裔學者奪“數學突破獎” 保持華人謙遜傳統|url=http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20140625/12754160.html|publisher=新浪網|date=2014-06-25|accessdate=2014-06-27|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304193437/http://news.sina.com.tw/article/20140625/12754160.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=2014數學突破獎揭曉，陶哲軒等5人各獲300萬美元|url=http://www.ibtimes.com.cn/trad/articles/37586/20140624/788004.htm|publisher=IBTimes|date=2014-06-24|accessdate=2014-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726180804/http://www.ibtimes.com.cn/trad/articles/37586/20140624/788004.htm|archive-date=2014-07-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

